song_name: Daddy Dont Live In That New York City No More
version_description: First chord version of this song.
Craicho 61 originally posted this and I made my corrections/changes that I think are correct by sound, not to take away from the original posting.
I'm using only triads, easier for beginners
The slash chords (D/E, C/F, G/C) are important for the Steely Dan sound. There are variations to these chords, but these fingerings sound close to the original recording.
Chord Sheet, emphasis on root notes and vocals.
